lead_paragraph: Gibraltar won a major battle in its fight for FIFA membership when football's governing body was ordered by sport's highest tribunal on Monday to reconsider the British territory's application that was rejected 20 months ago.

headline.print_headline: Big Gibraltar Win in Fight for FIFA Membership
